{"tid":116068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雙非母月花$4500租上水天台屋：對港家長不公平但「沒辦法」","createTime":"2017-02-11T05:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T06:00:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9542a45a5c9cd0706933f72d0b7d7d445a82f43","tid":116068,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170211/large/1486782482_ea46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170211%2Flarge%2F1486782482_ea46.jpg&h=5c69e875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170211/56289877\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170211%2F56289877&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2fleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=e14825e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170211%2F56289877&h=c939f2ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170211/56289877</a><br />\n<br />\n小一統一派位今、明兩天進行選校程序，原本居於深圳的雙非媽媽倪太太特意提早3、4個月來上水租房，務求有本港住址報讀北區80校網的上水小學，避過參加跨境校網，或被派至較遠地區。她表示每月花4,500元租上水的天台屋，比深圳的房子小很多，只放得下一張床及煮食器具，但她表示喜歡香港的教育，為了女兒來港上學，房子小一點也不介意。<br />\n<br />\n問到跨境學童本有專屬校網，透過租上水樓來報本港校網，是否對本港家長不公平，倪太太坦言「有一點」，但認為沒有辦法，因為自己希望女兒可以在港讀書，又指如果女兒派不到上水或粉嶺，派到較遠地區，會考慮讓女兒回深圳讀書。<br />\n本地家長高小姐則認為「教育局有政策，雙非及跨境家長有對策」，透過租上水樓甚至借假地址，搏入較鄰近學校。她認為雙非家長為子女著想無可厚非，但確實影響了本地學童入學機會。<br />\n高小姐認為長年加派學位令上水區失去小班教學，她指責早年小學殺校潮，認為政府早應把握時機推行小班，「政府放佢哋嚟（生育），但又無做好長遠規劃」。"},{"pid":"0cb3ce33ff839fded604aedf401ef0f05a1d0e0c","tid":116068,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:36:33.000Z","msg":"政府應該將跨境學童全部派去柴灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c05a85207842a0e967d11ac9fbb3e6a6a6a326","tid":116068,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f55fa59eca99d31ffd160508037264ec262cf0","tid":116068,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:43:07.000Z","msg":"港豬抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd8b8698e4d48a8763082f04cafd005962353ce","tid":116068,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}